title: Elizabeth Ann Classic
text:
The Elizabeth Ann Classic was a women's professional <a href="golf">golf</a> tournament on the <a href="Ladies%20European%20Tour">Ladies European Tour</a> held in <a href="England">England</a>. It was played in 1980 and 1981 at Pannal Golf Club, in <a href="Pannal">Pannal</a> near <a href="Harrogate">Harrogate</a>, <a href="North%20Yorkshire">North Yorkshire</a>.
Winners.
